room_title: Escape room "221B" by Clue'd In Escape Rooms in Columbus
review: Whoa, this was the best escape room I've ever done (I've done 3 so far)I'm a little bummed that our group didn't solve it, but the staff doesn't tell you the solution, so I could go back and try to finish it off. The combination of visual media, audio tech and good ol' fashioned trick safes and locks where seriously next level amazing!
